Thomas Anthony DeSimone -LRB- May 24 , 1950 -- disappeared January 14 , 1979 -RRB- , also known as Two-Gun Tommy or Tommy D , was a Sicilian-American gangster and associate of the Lucchese crime family in New York City .
DeSimone was a grandson and nephew of Los Angeles mob bosses Rosario DeSimone and Frank DeSimone , respectively .
He was married to Angelica `` Cookie '' Spione , but had many mistresses , including Theresa Ferrara .
In Martin Scorsese 's film Goodfellas , the character Tommy DeVito -LRB- portrayed by Joe Pesci -RRB- is based on DeSimone .